"<strong>Branches</strong> - You can think of Branches as \"partial\" graphs "
"that can be aggregated to form the \"full\" graph of a Resource Model. They "
"function as resuable building blocks, allowing you to avoid having to "
"manually recreate complex structures in multiple Resource Models."
